headline: ITT Stock Exhibits Strong Prospects Despite Persisting Headwinds
summary: ITT drives growth with acquisitions, strong demand across segments and shareholder returns despite higher costs and currency headwinds.

headline: 3M participates in JOINT3, a next-generation semiconductor packaging consortium
summary: 3M has joined the next-generation semiconductor packaging consortium JOINT3, an effort to bring together global leaders in semiconductor materials, equipment and design.
